    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/c88ed7e06a38f5d9eef86c23b5676362.poster.avif?t=1755282929\" width=600 height=686 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/c88ed7e06a38f5d9eef86c23b5676362.webm?t=1755282929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/c88ed7e06a38f5d9eef86c23b5676362.mp4?t=1755282929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The vast expanse of space has captivated humanity for ages, its enigmatic depths shrouded in secrets and puzzles that ignite the spark of curiosity and desire for exploration within us all. In SPACE SAGA, you have the opportunity to become a true space explorer, embarking on a thrilling adventure brimming with danger and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/f448016754bf444836cb94e0fa69e7c5.poster.avif?t=1755282929\" width=634 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/f448016754bf444836cb94e0fa69e7c5.webm?t=1755282929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/f448016754bf444836cb94e0fa69e7c5.mp4?t=1755282929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an interactive space simulator, you will assume the role of a skilled spaceship pilot and set off to explore the universe. Fly your ships through the cosmos, studying the unique features of the planets you encounter. But be wary, unexpected dangers may lurk in the void, requiring your skill and caution to navigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/762baffa1231f20be41bad23d57ea9c0.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>Travel through the cosmos, boldly discovering new worlds and facing treacherous factions that seek to impede your progress. But with a keen eye and steady hand, you can overcome any obstacle that comes your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/3a49c5ee213bb742a1a93c39fc2275d5.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>Forge your own destiny in this open world adventure. Collect resources and trade your way to success, or take a more aggressive approach, starting wars and raiding other ships. Find your path to the heart of the galaxy, carving out a legacy that will be remembered for ages to come. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/afa1b68ca62809bf0b30625b6cd8aca4.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>With three distinct classes of ships - Interceptors, Frigates, and Cruisers - at your disposal, you can customize your ride to suit your unique playstyle. Equip different modules that give your ship unparalleled abilities, and soar through the cosmos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/f62419d17f355dd14f9f494897007c15.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>As you progress, gather wealth and allies, building a fleet and team that will help you overcome any obstacle in your path. With your collective strength and cunning, you can achieve the ultimate goal: conquering the galaxy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/6becdce177cc28f5f0df874b946fe7d0.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>With partially dynamic generation, the game generates areas around you in real-time, creating a more immersive sense of space in the game. Furthermore, the world, events, and factions will be different every time you start a new game, adding a layer of replayability that will keep you coming back for more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375480/extras/6237a18b40e3e699425d7a0e853fb728.avif?t=1755282929\" width=620 height=80 /></span>Begin as a humble pilot, gradually expanding your knowledge and abilities. Join or create your own faction, managing it with care as you declare wars, trade goods, and ultimately aim to conquer the entire galaxy. The possibilities are endless, and the adventure is just beginning. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SPACE SAGA is a realistic yet fantastical game that transports you beyond the confines of everyday life, offering an escape to a thrilling and unforgettable adventure. Join the ranks of the great space explorers, and let the journey begin!</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文, 俄语, 日语, 法语, 土耳其语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 意大利语, 越南语, 印度尼西亚语, 韩语, 荷兰语, 波兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
